data.description: Step into Araby Crossing! This 3-bed, 2-bath beauty showcases timeless hardwood floors, grand vaulted ceilings, and a charming backyard – your retreat for morning coffee or summer BBQs. The paver-lined driveway adds a touch of elegance, setting the stage for interior opulence. Embrace the future with fixed solar panel payments of only $111! Priced at just $305,000, seize this opportunity to make a standout statement in the neighborhood and real estate market!
